00:48:27.410 --> 00:48:28.900
quite quickly.

00:48:28.900 --> 00:48:31.070
Yeah. There is -- Yes.

00:48:31.070 --> 00:48:34.180
There is a view that
there's that risk,

00:48:34.180 --> 00:48:40.790
and NIST has a program now for
developing encryption algorithms

00:48:40.790 --> 00:48:44.200
that would work in a
quantum computing world.

00:48:44.200 --> 00:48:48.890
So the U.S. government is
concerned that as demonstrated

00:48:48.890 --> 00:48:54.150
through the research they're
funding -- I think too --

00:48:54.150 --> 00:48:58.730
